This paper is primarily focused on natural language processing, which suggests that it is likely to be categorized under cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with machine learning models, which could place it under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper proposes a new approach to improve language models, which could place it under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the memory usage of language models, which could place it under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.SD (Sound).
